data.description: This charming two-story gem offers everything you've been looking for! Inside you will be greeted by the warmth of beautiful hardwood floors that stretch throughout the entire home! The open layout effortlessly connects the dining room and living room, creating a perfect space for gatherings with family and friends. Cozy up in the living room with a woodburning fireplace, adorned with elegant plantation shutters on the windows, adding a touch of sophistication. The kitchen is a chef's delight with its stunning 42" white shaker-style cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, you'll find four spacious bedrooms, including a serene primary suite with an en suite and walk-in closet. The laundry room upstairs makes household chores a breeze! Outside, the level-fenced backyard is perfect for outdoor activities, relaxation, and entertaining. Enjoy summer evenings under the inviting pergola, and host weekend bbqs with ease! Showings Start Sunday 4/28.
